pesquisaveis.valor: (select mat.MATRICULA from matriculafp mat where mat.PESSOA_ID = pf.ID and rownum <=1)

(select listagg(h.DESCRICAO, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY h.CODIGO)  from matriculafp matricula           inner join VINCULOFP vinculo ON vinculo.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.id and                                           vinculo.INICIOVIGENCIA = (select max(v.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                     from vinculofp v                                                                     where  v.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.ID)           inner join lotacaofuncional lot on lot.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and lot.inicioVigencia =                                                                                (select max(lota.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                 from LOTACAOFUNCIONAL lota                                                                                 where lota.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and rownum <=1)           inner join HIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL h                      on vinculo.UNIDADEORGANIZACIONAL_ID = h.SUBORDINADA_ID and                         h.TIPOHIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL = 'ADMINISTRATIVA' and                         sysdate between h.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(h.FIMVIGENCIA, sysdate)  where matricula.PESSOA_ID = pf.id)

(select listagg(h.CODIGO, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY h.CODIGO)  from matriculafp matricula           inner join VINCULOFP vinculo ON vinculo.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.id and                                           vinculo.INICIOVIGENCIA = (select max(v.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                     from vinculofp v                                                                     where  v.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.ID)           inner join lotacaofuncional lot on lot.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and lot.inicioVigencia =                                                                                (select max(lota.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                 from LOTACAOFUNCIONAL lota                                                                                 where lota.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and rownum <=1)           inner join HIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL h                      on vinculo.UNIDADEORGANIZACIONAL_ID = h.SUBORDINADA_ID and                         h.TIPOHIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL = 'ADMINISTRATIVA' and                         sysdate between h.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(h.FIMVIGENCIA, sysdate)  where matricula.PESSOA_ID = pf.id)

pf.ID in (case                     when ${VALOR_DIGITADO} ${OPERADOR} 'APOSENTADO' then (select mat.PESSOA_ID                                                                           from APOSENTADORIA apo                                                                                    inner join vinculofp v on apo.id = v.id                                                                                    inner join matriculafp mat on v.MATRICULAFP_ID = mat.ID                                                                           where mat.PESSOA_ID = obj.PESSOAFISICA_ID                                                                             and obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)                                                                             and ROWNUM = 1)                     when ${VALOR_DIGITADO} ${OPERADOR} 'PENSIONISTA' then (select mat.PESSOA_ID                                                                            from PENSIONISTA pen                                                                                     inner join vinculofp v on pen.id = v.id                                                                                     inner join matriculafp mat on v.MATRICULAFP_ID = mat.ID                                                                            where mat.PESSOA_ID = obj.PESSOAFISICA_ID                                                                              and obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)                                                                              and ROWNUM = 1)                     when ${VALOR_DIGITADO} ${OPERADOR} 'SERVIDOR' then (select mat.PESSOA_ID                                                                         from vinculofp vinculo                                                                                  inner join matriculafp mat on vinculo.MATRICULAFP_ID = mat.ID                                                                         where mat.PESSOA_ID = obj.PESSOAFISICA_ID                                                                           and obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between vinculo.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(vinculo.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)                                                                           and vinculo.id not in (select apo.id                                                                                                  from APOSENTADORIA apo                                                                                                           inner join vinculofp v on apo.id = v.id                                                                                                  where obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)                                                                                                    and v.id = vinculo.id)                                                                           and vinculo.id not in (select pen.id                                                                                                  from PENSIONISTA pen                                                                                                           inner join vinculofp v on pen.id = v.id                                                                                                  where obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)                                                                                                    and v.id = vinculo.id)                                                                           and ROWNUM = 1) end)

from:
from PessoaFisicaPortal obj
         inner join PessoaFisica pf on obj.PESSOAFISICA_ID = pf.ID

tabelaveis.valorOrdenacao: (select listagg(h.CODIGO || ' - ' || h.DESCRICAO, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY h.CODIGO)                  from matriculafp matricula                           inner join VINCULOFP vinculo ON vinculo.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.id and                                                           vinculo.INICIOVIGENCIA = (select max(v.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                     from vinculofp v                                                                                     where  v.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.ID)                           inner join lotacaofuncional lot on lot.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and lot.inicioVigencia =                                                                                                (select max(lota.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                                 from LOTACAOFUNCIONAL lota                                                                                                 where lota.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and rownum <=1)                           inner join HIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL h                                      on vinculo.UNIDADEORGANIZACIONAL_ID = h.SUBORDINADA_ID and                                         h.TIPOHIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL = 'ADMINISTRATIVA' and                                         sysdate between h.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(h.FIMVIGENCIA, sysdate)                  where matricula.PESSOA_ID = pf.id)
tabelaveis.valor: (select listagg(h.CODIGO || ' - ' || h.DESCRICAO, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY h.CODIGO)                  from matriculafp matricula                           inner join VINCULOFP vinculo ON vinculo.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.id and                                                           vinculo.INICIOVIGENCIA = (select max(v.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                     from vinculofp v                                                                                     where  v.MATRICULAFP_ID = matricula.ID)                           inner join lotacaofuncional lot on lot.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and lot.inicioVigencia =                                                                                                (select max(lota.INICIOVIGENCIA)                                                                                                 from LOTACAOFUNCIONAL lota                                                                                                 where lota.VINCULOFP_ID = vinculo.id and rownum <=1)                           inner join HIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL h                                      on vinculo.UNIDADEORGANIZACIONAL_ID = h.SUBORDINADA_ID and                                         h.TIPOHIERARQUIAORGANIZACIONAL = 'ADMINISTRATIVA' and                                         sysdate between h.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(h.FIMVIGENCIA, sysdate)                  where matricula.PESSOA_ID = pf.id)

tabelaveis.valorOrdenacao: case            when obj.DATAATUALIZACAO is not null then (select listagg(case                                                                          when (select apo.id                                                                                from APOSENTADORIA apo                                                                                where apo.id = v.ID and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Aposentado'                                                                          when (select pen.id                                                                                from PENSIONISTA pen                                                                                where pen.id = v.id and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Pensionista'                                                                          when (select c.id                                                                                from CONTRATOFP c                                                                                where c.id = v.id and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Servidor' end, ', ')                                                                      WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY v.id)                                                       from vinculofp v                                                                inner join MATRICULAFP mat on v.MATRICULAFP_ID = mat.ID                                                       where mat.PESSOA_ID = pf.id                                                         and obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)) end
tabelaveis.valor: case            when obj.DATAATUALIZACAO is not null then (select listagg(case                                                                          when (select apo.id                                                                                from APOSENTADORIA apo                                                                                where apo.id = v.ID and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Aposentado'                                                                          when (select pen.id                                                                                from PENSIONISTA pen                                                                                where pen.id = v.id and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Pensionista'                                                                          when (select c.id                                                                                from CONTRATOFP c                                                                                where c.id = v.id and ROWNUM = 1) is not null                                                                              then 'Servidor' end, ', ')                                                                      WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY v.id)                                                       from vinculofp v                                                                inner join MATRICULAFP mat on v.MATRICULAFP_ID = mat.ID                                                       where mat.PESSOA_ID = pf.id                                                         and obj.DATAATUALIZACAO between v.INICIOVIGENCIA and coalesce(v.FINALVIGENCIA, obj.DATAATUALIZACAO)) end
